Be sure to have ../inc made before making anything herein.

Programs:
kpzScaling 
	for basic (T)ASEP runs with optional auto correlation
kpzScalingCpu
	CPU version
kpzAutoResponse
	for auto-response runs
kpzAutoResponseCpu
	CPU version
cum
	compute higher order moments of scaling

CUDA codes are build for Tesla arch by default. Set the evironment variable
FERMI=on for Fermi and Kepler architechtures.
